K = 5
misScores = res.pca3$ind$coord[,1:K]
eig.val <- get_eigenvalue(res.pca3)
miT2 = colSums(t(misScores**2)/eig.val[1:K,1])
I = nrow(datos_eb1)
F95 = K*(I**2 - 1)/(I*(I - K)) * qf(0.95, K, I-K)
F99 = K*(I**2 - 1)/(I*(I - K)) * qf(0.99, K, I-K)

plot(1:length(miT2), miT2, type = "p", xlab = "News", ylab = "T2")
abline(h = F95, col = "orange", lty = 2, lwd = 2)
abline(h = F99, col = "red3", lty = 2, lwd = 2)

anomalas_1 = which(miT2 > F95)

## HCB_w12_ni        0.08 -0.02  0.12  0.02
## bHCH_w12_ni       0.15 -0.01  0.16  0.10
## PCBtotal3_w12_ni  0.05  0.12  0.08  0.20
K = 10
misScores = res.pca4$ind$coord[,1:K]
eig.val <- get_eigenvalue(res.pca4)
miT2 = colSums(t(misScores**2)/eig.val[1:K,1])
I = nrow(datos_eb1)
F95 = K*(I**2 - 1)/(I*(I - K)) * qf(0.95, K, I-K)
F99 = K*(I**2 - 1)/(I*(I - K)) * qf(0.99, K, I-K)

plot(1:length(miT2), miT2, type = "p", xlab = "News", ylab = "T2")
abline(h = F95, col = "orange", lty = 2, lwd = 2)
abline(h = F99, col = "red3", lty = 2, lwd = 2)

anomalas_2 = which(miT2 > F95)
